Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=10}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:57.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Hey, wait, Franky! - OG}Ei, Franky, espera!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:00.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Huh? What is... - OG}Hã? O que–{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:02.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At least put some pants on! - OG}Pelo menos veste uma calça antes de sair!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:05.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Geez... Didn't you learn a lesson the first time? - OG}Sério, não aprendeu\Nnada da primeira vez?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:08.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you go to town with only a swimsuit on, there'll be another perv uproar, right? - OG}Só de sunga vai causar\Noutra confusão de tarado, sabia?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:12.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Geez... I'm just going shopping. - OG}Ah, é só pra fazer umas compras.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:14.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, go already! - OG}Vai logo, então.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:19.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Geez... To think that she's\Ntaking the trouble to prepare celebration dishes just because\NTom-san is being declared not guilty... - OG}Que besteira, preparar toda essa refeição só pra comemorar a absolvição do Tom...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:22.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He wasn't guilty from the start. - OG}Quer dizer, ele era inocente\Ndesde o começo.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now... - OG}Agora, então...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:31.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Tom-san! Iceburg! Get up! - OG}Ei, Tom e Iceburg! Levantem!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Today is the trial day! - OG}Hoje é o dia do julgamento!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:35.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurry up and go get judged! - OG}Vão logo ser julgados!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:40.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurry to the harbor! - OG}Rápido pro cais!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:41.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom's sentence is going to be be handed down! - OG}Vão dar o veredito do Tom!{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:52.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This trial seems to be of\Nhigh interest to the people. - OG}Bela multidão pra esse julgamento.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:56.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A lot of court spectators are getting on board. - OG}Os espectadores estão embarcando em massa.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Have you seen the sea train, judge? - OG}Já viu o sea train, Meritíssimo?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I took a ride once. - OG}Sim. Andei nele uma vez.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:04.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's indeed incredible. I'm impressed\Nthat he really made it happen. - OG}É maravilhoso. Uma conquista\Nrealmente impressionante.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora que as quatro ilhas estão conectadas,{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:10.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I imagine no one would oppose his acquittal. - OG}duvido que alguém se oponha à absolvição dele.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:11.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Tom já chegou?{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:13.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mal posso esperar pra começar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:16.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurry! The spectators' gallery is gonna fill up! - OG}Rápido, antes da galeria de espectadores lotar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:19.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! I have to see the moment he is\Ndeclared not guilty with my own eyes! - OG}Isso aí! Quero ver ele ser\Nabsolvido com meus próprios olhos!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:24.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This brings back memories.\NIt's already been 14 years, huh? - OG}Puxa, já fazem quatorze anos.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:39.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What're these explosions?! - OG}O quê?! Explosões?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get off the ship! Hurry! Hurry up! - OG}Saiam do navio! Todos, rápido!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:51.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's going on?! A pirate raid?! - OG}Isso é algum tipo de ataque pirata?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! Where are they firing from?! - OG}Droga! De onde estão vindo esses tiros?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm?! Over there! - OG}Hã...? Ali!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's that fleet?! - OG}De quem é aquela frota?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:03.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:12.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've never seen battleships like them!\NWhich pirate group is that?! - OG}Nunca vi navios de guerra assim!\NDe que grupo pirata são?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:17.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What the hell is with those\Nheavily armed ships?! - OG}Que diabos são esses?!\NEstão cobertos de armas!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get away from the harbor! Hurry up and run! - OG}Afastem-se do cais! Rápido, corram!{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Run towards the town! - OG}Corram pro centro da cidade!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:29.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Help! My son is stuck! - OG}Socorro! Meu filho está sendo pisoteado!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:39.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who the hell... - OG}Quem é...?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:46.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{took... - OG}M-Meus...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{took my ships?! - OG}Meus navios...!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san! There's trouble! - OG}Tom, temos problemas!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? - OG}Hã?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:54.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Franky's ships are attacking the Judicial Ship! - OG}Os navios do Franky estão atacando o navio judicial!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:57.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait! It's not Franky. He's in town right now. - OG}Calma. Não pode ser o Franky.\NEle acabou de ir pra cidade.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:01.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He certainly wouldn't do something\Nlike that! I know that much. - OG}Eu sei! Nem ele faria\Nalgo assim.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Exatamente por isso que é um problema!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll stop them, Iceburg! - OG}Vamos impedi-los, Iceburg!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:05.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! - OG}Tá!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:10.58,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are they pirates? Or someone\Nfrom the Government? - OG}Piratas...? Ou talvez o governo...?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:13.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Evacuem!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't stop! Hurry inland! - OG}Não parem! Vão mais pro interior!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get away from the harbor! - OG}Afastem-se das docas!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{My father is still inside! - OG}Meu pai ainda está no navio!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:25.18,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Bastards! - OG}Malditos!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.43,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{They won't get away with this! - OG}Não posso permitir isso!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.06,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! Who are they?! - OG}Droga! Quem são eles?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.81,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem está zoando com meus navios?!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Judge! Please hurry up!\NThis ship won't hold out! - OG}Meritíssimo, rápido! O navio não vai aguentar!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:47.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who does that fleet belong to? - OG}De quem são esses navios?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The raid on the Judicial Ship was successful. - OG}O ataque ao navio judicial foi um sucesso.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:56.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see... Then move on to the next\Nstep in the scenario immediately. - OG}Entendo. Então passem\Npara a próxima etapa do plano.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a sacrifice for justice. - OG}A justiça exige sacrifícios.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:05:59.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:07.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, let's start the trial... - OG}Então, vamos começar seu julgamento {\i1}agora{\i0}...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tom's Workers...{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:18.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Judicial Ship will sink soon. - OG}O navio judicial está afundando.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:20.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, then! Let's go back\Nto the scrap heap island! - OG}Certo. Vamos recuar pra Ilha do Ferro-Velho.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:21.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, a frota está recuando!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:31.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait... I recognize those ships! - OG}Espera... Eu conheço esses navios!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san! The ships are coming back this way! - OG}Tom, os navios estão voltando.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're close to the shore!\NI think we can catch them! - OG}Estão perto da costa. Dá pra pegá-los!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They sure went and did\Nsomething crazy with those ships! - OG}É de loucura o que fizeram com esses navios!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:48.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Two people are running this way\Nfrom the scrap heap island! - OG}Dois homens da Ilha do Ferro-Velho estão vindo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, then! Let's leave the ship. - OG}Certo! Abandonem o navio.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What the...?! - OG}Que diabos?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No one is on the ships. - OG}Não tem ninguém a bordo.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This side, too. No one is on any of the ships! - OG}Aqui também. Estão todos desertos.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:09.41,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom... O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:12.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esses são do Franky também.{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:15.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ahh! Iceburg! Watch out! - OG}Ah não! Iceburg, cuidado!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit...! - OG}Droga...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:33.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{My Battle Frankys are a mess! - OG}Meus Battle Frankies foram destruídos!{JT}
Comment: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:37.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg! Tom-san! - OG}Iceburg! Tom!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Both of you...! - OG}Ei, vocês dois...!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's going on?! What happened?! - OG}O que houve?! O que aconteceu?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you okay?! - OG}Vocês estão bem?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Ice-- - OG}Fala alguma coisa, Ice–{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You idiot! - OG}Seu imbecil!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:13.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That intelligence agent\Nwho came the other day... - OG}Aqueles agentes de inteligência\Nque vieram outro dia...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:16.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They used your battleships. - OG}Usaram seus navios de guerra contra a gente!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:20.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You got hurt by my battleships?! - OG}M-Meus navios fizeram isso com vocês?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I told you, didn't I? - OG}Eu avisei.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Over... and over again... - OG}Várias... e várias vezes...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:30.45,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(21,300,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}{I can't understand your nerve,\Njust leaving dozens of them out here! - OG}Não entendo como você pode deixar\Ndezenas dessas coisas espalhadas por aí.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:35.16,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm calling you to account for\Ncreating lethal weapons, Moron-ky! - OG}Você é culpado por criar\Nessas armas, Franburro!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:38.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san got... hurt by my ships! - OG}Meus navios... fizeram aquilo com o Tom?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:40.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Listen. - OG}Entenda...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Our skills can bring lethal\Nweapons into this world... - OG}As armas que criamos são letais.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:47.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...even if you don't intend to do so. - OG}Tenha você a intenção ou não,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:51.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Weapons hurt people despite your intentions! - OG}armas não se importam com quem machucam.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:55.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They can even hurt those\Nwho mean a lot to you! - OG}Mesmo que seja alguém que você ama!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:09:00.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We were taken in by the Government. - OG}O governo nos incriminou.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:03.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're gonna make us the culprits\Nfor attacking the Judicial Ship... - OG}Vão nos acusar do ataque ao navio judicial.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:09.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...because they want to question Tom-san\Nas a criminal to obtain the blueprints. - OG}Para conseguir as plantas, eles precisam que o Tom\Nseja tratado como criminoso e interrogado.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:14.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After all this... can you still\Nsay that you're innocent?! - OG}Depois de tudo isso, ainda pode\Nse dizer inocente?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:17.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we can't somehow stop them\Nfrom taking Tom-san away... - OG}Se não conseguirmos impedir\Nque levem o Tom embora...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...I'll never... - OG}eu nunca...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:23.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...forgive you for the rest of my life, Franky! - OG}vou te perdoar, Franky!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:29.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll never-- - OG}Eu nunca...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it! - OG}Já chega!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:32.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san... - OG}Tom!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não culpe ele, Iceburg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not Franky's fault. - OG}A culpa não é do Franky.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're still saying that, even at this point?! - OG}Como pode dizer isso numa hora dessas?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san! - OG}Tom!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa! Eu fiz esse arpão.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:50.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I made it so that it can't come\Nout once it pierces its target! - OG}Fiz ele pra não sair depois de penetrar.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:51.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:56.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't apologize. This is nothing. - OG}Não precisa se desculpar! É só um arranhão.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olhem, eles estão ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom is on the ground! - OG}O Tom caiu!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why is he seriously injured like that?! - OG}Como se machucou tanto assim?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:05.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then, it wasn't them who made the raid? - OG}Então não foram eles que atacaram.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The townspeople are here. - OG}São os moradores da cidade.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, então,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:16.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...shall we head to the town, too? - OG}acho que devemos ir pra cidade também.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You bastard, Spanda! - OG}Maldito, Spanda!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:20.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's "Spandam"... - OG}É Spanda{\i1}m{\i0}.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:23.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...you criminals... - OG}Esses criminosos...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{These are the raid culprits. - OG}são os responsáveis pelo ataque!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Please rest easy, everyone. - OG}Podem ficar tranquilos, senhoras e senhores.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:34.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We, CP5, brought them down\Nafter they made the raid. - OG}Nós da CP5 os capturamos\Napós o ataque.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They can't cause any more trouble. - OG}Não são mais uma ameaça.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He would've been found\Nnot guilty in today's trial... - OG}As acusações do Tom estavam\Nprestes a ser retiradas no julgamento de hoje.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:42.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So then, why did Tom do something like that? - OG}Por que ele faria algo assim?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:45.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So he was a friend of the\NKing of the Pirates after all, huh? - OG}Parece que ele realmente estava\Nnisso com o Rei dos Piratas.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Pleased to meet you. - OG}Prazer em conhecê-lo.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm Spandam from CP5.- OG}Sou Spandam, da CP5.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:53.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You happened to be there?\NThank you. You saved us. - OG}Não sabia que estava aqui.\NObrigado pela ajuda.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:56.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Please hand them over to us, - OG}Vamos precisar que esses homens\Nfiquem sob nossa custódia.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{as we would like to investigate them. - OG}Gostaríamos de interrogá-los.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:05.10,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Try making excuses if you like.\NOur trustworthiness is worlds apart. - OG}Tente se justificar se quiser.\NSua credibilidade já era.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:09.61,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll get the blueprints of the ancient weapon. - OG}Eu, Spandam, terei as plantas da arma ancestral.{Gaijin}
Comment: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:10.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ribbit, ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How terrible... - OG}Que desastre...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:19.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{First, about the sea train,\Nall I can say is, splendid. - OG}Primeiro, devo dizer que o sea train\Né simplesmente espetacular.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:24.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can see it'll contribute greatly\Nto the growth of Water Seven. - OG}Tenho certeza que contribuirá muito\Npara a crescente prosperidade de Water 7.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:29.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{For that, on the previous charge\Nfor building Gold Roger's ship, - OG}Pela acusação anterior\Nde construir o navio de Gold Roger,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:34.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{your acquittal today had\Npretty much been decided. - OG}isso por si só era suficiente pra justificar\Nsua absolvição hoje.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So then, why did you commit another crime? - OG}Então por que cometer outro crime?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's a load of crap! - OG}Que besteira!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:40.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're not the ones who\Nraided the Judicial Ship! - OG}Não fomos nós que atacamos o navio judicial!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:43.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was that Spandam guy who did it! - OG}Foi aquele maldito Spandam ali!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:49.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:51.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No way! - OG}Tá brincando?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:54.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's got into that disciple of Tom's,\Nsuddenly cracking jokes? - OG}O que o aprendiz do Tom está dizendo?{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:12:00.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What would CP5, a Government entity,\Ngain by sinking a Judicial Ship? - OG}O que a agência governamental CP5\Nganharia afundando o navio judicial?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:04.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What a stupid thing to say!\NThat's not possible at all! - OG}Ridículo. Isso é simplesmente impossível.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:07.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cutty Flam, não é?{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:14.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To start with, we caught you\Nred-handed on one of the raid ships. - OG}Não vamos esquecer que te pegamos\Nem flagrante num dos navios do ataque.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:20.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In addition, weren't those raid\Nships built by your company? - OG}Além disso, sua empresa construiu\Ntodos aqueles navios, certo?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ships that would do something like that... - OG}Navios que causaram tal estrago...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:33.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're... no longer... - OG}Esses... não são mais...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,meus navios!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom tore his handcuffs apart! - OG}O Tom arrebentou as algemas!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ready! - OG}Preparar armas!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:57.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san... hit Franky for the first time... - OG}É a primeira vez...\Nque o Tom bate no Franky...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:58.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What'd you do that for?! - OG}Que diabos foi isso?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{"They're no longer my ships," you say? - OG}"Esses não são mais meus navios"?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can say anything but that! - OG}Essa é a única coisa que nunca pode dizer!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:12.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's wrong with saying that?!\NI'm regretting it! - OG}Qual o problema com isso?!\NEstou me arrependendo de tudo!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:16.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If only those ships didn't exist,\Nno one would have had to get hurt! - OG}Se eu nunca tivesse feito esses navios,\Nninguém teria se machucado!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:21.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não importa que tipo de navio seja,\No ato de construí-lo...{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:27.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,não é nem bom nem mau!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:31.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't care what kind of\Nships you choose to build, - OG}Não me importa que tipo de navio você construa.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:32.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but... - OG}Porém,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:38.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{even if the ships you built hurt someone, or even if they destroy the world, - OG}não importa quem eles machuquem\Nou como ameacem o mundo,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:41.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{at least the one who created\Nthem must love them! - OG}você, como criador deles, deve amá-los.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:45.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Their creator mustn't deny them! - OG}Não deve negar o que criou.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't blame the ships! - OG}Nunca culpe o navio!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:52.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A man should be resolutely proud...\Nof the ships he created! - OG}Um homem deve ter {\i1}muito{\i0} orgulho\Ndos navios que constrói!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:14.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Iceburg... Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:18.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't interfere\Nin what I'm about to do... - OG}não interfiram no que vou fazer agora...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:19.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter what. - OG}não importa o quê!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:27.04,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's the World Government who pinned the crime on us. It's also the World Government who judges it. - OG}Primeiro, o Governo Mundial me incrimina.\NE agora me julga.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.62,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no way that we'll\Nget cleared of suspicion. - OG}Não tem como limpar meu nome agora...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.18,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is it. - OG}É assim que termina.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:37.69,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{It must be really tough for you to see\Nyour innocent ships being used like this. - OG}Deve ser duro ver seus navios\Ninocentes usados pra algo assim.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:41.07,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{You must want to beat up\Nthat guy, right, Franky? - OG}Aposto que quer bater nele, Franky.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:52.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san! - OG}Tom!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom started going on a rampage! - OG}O Tom está enlouquecendo!{Z}
Comment: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:55.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, my God... - OG}O que ele está fazendo?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Please stop! If you lay\None more finger on him...! - OG}Para! Se continuar assim...!{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:03.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...understand the pain he's feeling?! - OG}faz ideia do quanto\Nmachucoou aquele garoto?!{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:07.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,F-Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atiram nele...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san! - OG}Tom!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.07,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tranquillizer bullets, huh? - OG}Dardos tranquilizantes, né?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:34.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You damn fishman with superhuman\Nstrength! That serves you right! - OG}Toma essa, seu homem-peixe monstruoso!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san! Why'd you do that?! - OG}Tom, por que fez aquilo?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:41.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, guys! What're you doing?!\NHurry up and capture them! - OG}Ei, seus idiotas, o que estão fazendo?!\NPrendam eles já!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:45.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll take everyone from the ferocious\NTom's Workers company to Enies Lobby! - OG}Levem esses selvagens da\NTom's Workers pra Enies Lobby!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:48.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think that Tom is such a dangerous person... - OG}Não sabia que o Tom era tão violento.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What the hell is he thinking?! - OG}O que ele está pensando?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:54.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He really sold his soul to pirates! - OG}Sabia que tinha se vendido pros piratas!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:58.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He made that many battleships and\Nwaited for an opportunity like this! - OG}Construíram aqueles navios de guerra\Njustamente pra isso!{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You bastards! How dare you\Ntalk like that to Tom-san?! - OG}Como podem falar assim do Tom?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it. - OG}Deixe.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:03.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's all right. - OG}Está tudo bem.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:05.74,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:07.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Judge... - OG}Meritíssimo.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:08.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? - OG}Sim?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:13.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll confess to the charge of\Nmaking a raid on the Judicial Ship. - OG}Confesso a culpa pelo ataque ao navio judicial.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Tom-san! Don't! - OG}Espera! Tom, retire o que disse!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:18.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I have a favor to ask. - OG}Porém, tenho um pedido.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:22.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up, you stupid fishman! Who'd listen to a criminal's... - OG}Cale a boca, seu homem-peixe idiota!\NQuem atenderia o pedido de um criminoso?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:23.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Keep your mouth shut, CP5! - OG}Silêncio, CP5!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:24.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:27.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So, what is the favor? - OG}Qual é seu pedido?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:32.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I can get one charge eliminated\Nfor our building the sea train... - OG}Se posso ter um crime absolvido\Npor construir o sea train...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...I'd like today's charge to be eliminated. - OG}peço que seja o crime de hoje.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:36.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? - OG}Hã?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:41.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if that wish is granted,\Nyou'll just go back to square one. - OG}Se eu atender seu pedido,\Nvocê volta à estaca zero.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:46.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You'll end up with the crime of building a ship for the King of the Pirates, which will result in the maximum penalty. - OG}Ainda seria culpado por construir o navio\Ndo Rei dos Piratas, crime capital.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:49.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I prefer that. - OG}Isso mesmo. Prefiro assim.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:52.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{About assisting that Roger guy... - OG}É, eu ajudei o homem chamado Roger.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:56.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm resolutely proud of it! - OG}Tenho {\i1}muito{\i0} orgulho disso!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How selfish... - OG}Que egoísmo...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:03.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think that he's proud of\Nassisting the King of the Pirates... - OG}Imagina ter orgulho de ajudar\No Rei dos Piratas...{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Traitor! - OG}Ele é um traidor!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{--Ferocious fishman!\N--Damn fishman! - OG}– Homem-peixe covarde!\N– Maldito homem-peixe!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:09.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san... Why?! - OG}Tom... Por quê?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's fine. - OG}Estou bem com isso.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Listen. Don't blame yourself, okay? - OG}Escute. Não se culpe.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:20.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I never thought that the Government\Nwould use force to get the blueprints. - OG}Não tinha ideia de que o governo estava\Ntão determinado a obter as plantas.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:23.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was at a bit of a disadvantage\Ndue to the matter with Roger. - OG}Meu trabalho com Roger me colocou\Nem desvantagem.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:25.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas mesmo assim, você não precisava–{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry. - OG}Está tudo bem.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:33.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Look at the town. Even if my charge goes back to what it was 14 years ago, everything is different from then. - OG}Olhe, mesmo que as acusações voltem catorze anos,\Ntudo mudou desde então.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This island is full of energy now. - OG}A ilha ganhou vida.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é só o começo.{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:43.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não importa o que aconteça comigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:46.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can be of help to the town. - OG}ainda serei útil pra cidade.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:49.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{My dream has... - OG}Meu sonho...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:54.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...finally... begun to run. - OG}finalmente... saiu da estação.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san! - OG}Tom!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san! - OG}Tom!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:08.32,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Iceburg... Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:11.11,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Take care of the blueprints. - OG}cuidem das plantas.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.36,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kokoro-san... Yokozuna... - OG}Dona Kokoro... Yokozuna...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.53,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thanks for everything. - OG}obrigado por tudo.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The tranquillizer bullets have finally started working! - OG}Os tranquilizantes fizeram efeito!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Capture those three culprits\Nfor the Judicial Ship raid! - OG}Prendam esses três\Npelo ataque ao navio judicial!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:27.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:29.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hold it! - OG}Cancelem essa ordem.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm changing the charges. - OG}As acusações mudaram.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:38.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{For the charge of building the pirate ship\Nfor Gold Roger, King of the Pirates, - OG}Pelo crime de construir o navio pirata\Ndo Rei dos Piratas Gold Roger,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:42.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{we'll take shipbuilding\Nengineer Tom to Enies Lobby. - OG}escoltaremos o carpinteiro naval\NTom até Enies Lobby.{Z/PP/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:43.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:50.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What got into that old geezer? - OG}O que deu naquele velho sentimental?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:52.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, well. I don't have\Nbusiness with his disciples. - OG}Tanto faz. Não preciso dos aprendizes dele.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:54.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Release those two disciples! - CR}Libertem os dois aprendizes!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:03.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san can no longer be saved. - OG}O Tom não pode mais ser salvo.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:07.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If it's the World Government we're\Nup against, there's nothing we can do! - OG}Não há nada que possamos fazer\Ncontra o Governo Mundial.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:12.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Bear it. Tom-san saved you two! - OG}Sejam fortes, vocês dois.\NO Tom salvou a vida de vocês!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:17.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you make an enemy of them, no matter how many lives\Nyou have, it's not enough! - OG}Se os fizerem de inimigos,\Nestarão mortos antes do fim do dia.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:20.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Enies Lobby is the judicial island\Nowned by the Government. - OG}Enies Lobby, a Ilha Judicial,\Npertence ao governo.{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:27.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No criminals taken there... ...have ever returned! - OG}Nenhum dos criminosos\Nenviados pra lá jamais voltou!{yag/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The sea train is ready! - OG}O sea train está pronto pra partir!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We can take him now! - OG}Podemos ir!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Good! - OG}Certo!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kokoro-san... - OG}Dona Kokoro...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:38.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, you guys! Hurry up and take away... - OG}Ei, vocês! Tirem ele daqui agora!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:39.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...this heavy, crazy fishman! - OG}Esse... homem-peixe... pesado e louco!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:46.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't do that! - OG}...não aguento mais!{Gaijin}
Comment: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:46.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ribbit!
Comment: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:47.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:49.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it! - OG}Franky, não!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Spandam-san's face got bent! - OG}Ele arrebentou a cara do agente Spandam!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:09.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This time, Tom's disciple\Nstarted going on a rampage! - OG}Agora é o aprendiz do Tom\Nque está enlouquecendo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it! - OG}Já chega!{Gaijin}
Comment: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:11.90,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ribbit, ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:16.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Capture him! The rest of you, take Tom away! - OG}Prendam ele! O resto, levem o Tom!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:20.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Fine by me! I won't let you take him away! - OG}Tenta! Não vou deixar vocês levarem ele!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:21.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're allowed to shoot him! - OG}Autorizado a atirar!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:24.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give us Tom-san back! - OG}Soltem o Tom!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurry up and run! - OG}Corre!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:34.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:47.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Ele escapou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:51.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll never let that Cutty Flam\Nbrat get away with this! - OG}Nunca vou perdoar aquele moleque, Cutty Flam!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He is truly a criminal! - OG}Ele é um criminoso de verdade!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:57.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Once this case is over,\NI'll have him sent to the gallows! - OG}Quando isso acabar, vou mandar\Naquele idiota pra forca!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Spandam-san! - OG}Agente Spandam!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.07,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you want?! - OG}O quê?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I-É o Cutty Flam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! - OG}Como assim?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:05.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He came this far after us! - OG}Ele nos interceptou!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:09.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's standing on the railway with some weapon! - OG}Está nos trilhos à frente\Ncom algum tipo de arma.{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stay there, Yokozuna. - OG}Espera aqui, Yokozuna.{Gaijin}
Comment: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:16.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rib-Ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:19.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is he stupid or what? - OG}Ele é imbecil?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:20.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What should we do? - OG}Qual é a ordem?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:22.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you stupid, too?! - OG}{\i1}Você{\i0} também é imbecil?!{JT}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:26.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just keep going; give him what he wants. - OG}Continue em frente!\NVamos dar o que ele quer.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be concerned about him! - OG}Ele não é relevante!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Sim, senhor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:34.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para, {\i1}Puffing Tom{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:40.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where are you taking your creator to?! - OG}Pra onde está levando\No homem que te criou?!{Gaijin}
Comment: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:52.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ribbit, ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:57.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't let you pass here! - OG}Fim da linha!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:04.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give Tom-san back to us! - OG}Me devolvam o Tom!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:09.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2910,3760,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Pare, sea train!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:18.02,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see. Your parents abandoned you, huh? That's so funny! - OG}Seus pais te largaram? Hilário!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:20.03,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, you're laughing too hard! - OG}Ei, não ri tanto!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:22.78,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, then! Come resolutely to my place! - OG}Bom, você é {\i0}muito{\i1} bem-vindo na minha casa.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:24.70,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san... - OG}Tom...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:28.66,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't wanna build ships anymore! - OG}pra ser sincero... não quero\Nmais construir navios.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:34.71,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't love ships that hurt\Nthe people I really care about! - OG}Não consigo amar um navio que machucou\Nalguém precioso pra mim!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:36.29,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{But, Tom-san... - OG}Mas, Tom...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:41.46,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{...you're my goal after all! - OG}eu ainda quero ser como você!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:53.79,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{So I want you to come back\Nand teach me again... - OG}Quero que você volte\Ne continue me ensinando!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.31,0:23:04.95,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{...because I want to... - OG}Eu também,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:07.70,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{...build a dream ship someday, too. - OG}quero construir meu navio dos sonhos!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:17.37,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{A ship that resolutely and proudly traverses even uncharted waves at edges of the earth! - OG}Um navio... que orgulhosamente cruze\Naté ondas inexploradas pelo mundo todo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:19.94,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{A dream ship like that! - OG}Esse é meu navio dos sonhos!{Gaijin}
